<item>
            <title>[SOLR-3122] RecoveryStrat can not use interrupt due to the use of Channels.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3122</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;along the lines of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2239&quot; title=&quot;Revise NIOFSDirectory and its usage due to NIO limitations on Thread.interrupt&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LUCENE-2239&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LUCENE-2239&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, we cannot use interrupt unfortunetly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12542259">SOLR-3122</key>
            <summary>RecoveryStrat can not use interrupt due to the use of Channels.</summary>
